The purpose of this app is help construction managers deal with compliance for climate related regulations. If the air quality is bad, then the manager needs to complete certain tasks. 

There will be multiple sites per manager, for example, on in NYC and one in LA. A navbar will be used to switch between then, and a searchbar will be able the list on the navbar to search for other sites.

The main call to action is in the tasks. Example tasks will include:
- distributing masks to workers
- updating equipment
- notifying onsite manager
- reviewing report

